scenes.description: Group performance of the song 'Identity' by Kanaria. Aki Rosenthal performs with Hololive members.
Visual interlude with 'Life is GAME' graphics and Aki Rosenthal dancing solo.
Aki Rosenthal performs 'Bad Apple!!' on a black and white spiral stage.

subtitles.original: イカせてあげる Ah
subtitles.english: I'll let you go, Ah.

subtitles.original: やってきた感慨な
subtitles.english: The deep emotion that has arrived.

subtitles.original: アタシがついてるから
subtitles.english: Because I'm here with you.

subtitles.original: Everybody say I want to be free
subtitles.english: Everybody say I want to be free.

subtitles.original: この美徳習慣 全部黙らす Show
subtitles.english: This virtuous custom, a show to silence it all.

subtitles.original: 目覚ませ起きろ
subtitles.english: Wake up, get up!

subtitles.original: 生きてるんだだし
subtitles.english: Since I'm alive.

subtitles.original: ねえ 生きてるんだだし
subtitles.english: Hey, since I'm alive.

subtitles.original: 生まれたその時から選んできたんだ思い出せ
subtitles.english: Remember, I chose this from the moment I was born.

subtitles.original: アタシはアタシだ
subtitles.english: I am me.

subtitles.original: 不可能なことなど何一つもない そうじゃないの
subtitles.english: There's nothing impossible, isn't that right?

subtitles.original: 生まれたその時から選んできたんだ思い出せ
subtitles.english: Remember, I chose this from the moment I was born.

subtitles.original: 貴方は貴方だ
subtitles.english: You are you.

subtitles.original: 不可能なことなど何一つもない そうじゃないの
subtitles.english: There's nothing impossible, isn't that right?

subtitles.original: 愛いっぱい自分に
subtitles.english: Full of love for myself.

subtitles.original: 好き嫌い常識 I don't care ぶっ飛ばせ
subtitles.english: Likes, dislikes, common sense, I don't care, blast them away!

subtitles.original: Again 好き嫌い常識 I don't care ぶっ飛ばせ
subtitles.english: Again, likes, dislikes, common sense, I don't care, blast them away!

subtitles.original: 流れてく時の中ででも
subtitles.english: Even within the flowing time,

subtitles.original: 気だるさがほらグルグル廻って
subtitles.english: look, the lethargy spins round and round.

subtitles.original: 私から離れる心も見えないわ
subtitles.english: I can't even see my heart leaving me.

subtitles.original: そう知らない
subtitles.english: I really don't know.

subtitles.original: 自分から動くこともなく
subtitles.english: Without moving on my own,

subtitles.original: 時の隙間に流され続けて
subtitles.english: I continue to be swept away in the gaps of time.

subtitles.original: 知らないわ周りのことなど
subtitles.english: I don't know anything about what's around me.

subtitles.original: 私は私それだけ
subtitles.english: I am me, that is all.

subtitles.original: 夢見てる？なにも見てない？
subtitles.english: Am I dreaming? Am I seeing nothing?

subtitles.original: 語るも無駄な自分の言葉
subtitles.english: My own words are useless to speak.

subtitles.original: 悲しむなんて疲れるだけよ
subtitles.english: Being sad just makes me tired.

subtitles.original: 何も感じず過ごせばいいの
subtitles.english: It's fine if I spend time feeling nothing.

subtitles.original: 戸惑う言葉与えられても
subtitles.english: Even if given confusing words,

subtitles.original: 自分の心ただ上の空
subtitles.english: my heart is just absent-minded.

subtitles.original: もし私から動くのならば
subtitles.english: If I were to move on my own,

subtitles.original: すべて変えるのなら黒にする
subtitles.english: if I could change everything, I'd turn it black.

subtitles.original: こんな自分に未来はあるの？
subtitles.english: Does such a self have a future?

subtitles.original: こんな世界に私はいるの？
subtitles.english: Am I existing in such a world?

subtitles.original: 今切ないの？今悲しいの？
subtitles.english: Is it painful now? Is it sad now?

subtitles.original: 自分の事もわからないまま
subtitles.english: While not even understanding myself.

subtitles.original: 歩むことさえ疲れるだけよ
subtitles.english: Even walking just tires me out.

subtitles.original: 人のことなど知りもしないわ
subtitles.english: I don't know anything about others.

subtitles.original: こんな私も変われるのなら
subtitles.english: If even I can change,

subtitles.original: もし変われるのなら白になる
subtitles.english: if I can change, I'll become white.
